"2 cups (1 lb.) unsalted butter, softened","1/4 cup chopped mixed fresh herbs (such as parsley, oregano, dill, tarragon, rosemary)","1/4 cup  minced shallot","1 Tbsp.  lemon zest, plus 1 Tbsp. fresh juice (from 2 lemons)","2 tsp.  anchovy paste","1 tsp.  kosher salt","1/2 tsp.  black pepper","8 oz.  fingerling potatoes, cut in half lengthwise","1/4 cup water","1 1/2 lb.  hanger steak, at room temperature","1/2 tsp.  black pepper","2 tsp.  kosher salt, divided","2 tsp.  olive oil","2 Tbsp.  unsalted butter","2 tsp.  fresh lemon juice (from 1 lemon)","8 oz.  fresh Brussels sprouts, cut in half","1  small yellow onion, cut into vertical 1/4-in. slices"